jspreprocessor:test-preprocessors

Full name:

com.github.jlgrock.javascript-framework:jspreprocessor-maven-plugin:1.5:test-preprocessors

Description:

eventually, this should do a bunch of things, but right now, it will just copy from src/main/javascript to /target/javascript-generated.

Attributes:

  • Requires a Maven 2.0 project to be executed.

Optional Parameters

Name Type Since Description
frameworkTargetDirectory File - (no description)
Default value is: ${project.build.directory}${file.separator}javascriptframework.
sourceDirectory File - (no description)
Default value is: ${project.basedir}${file.separator}src${file.separator}test${file.separator}javascript.
